  "firstAcquaintance": "The universally acknowledged current Sword Saint. Acts on a whim -- she will cut down anything she dislikes regardless of the other party's power, and thus has been designated a 'Natural Disaster'.",
  "personality": "Eccentric and impulsive, difficult to read. Highly self-willed, with a sense of right and wrong that differs from others. Respects those who follow through on their convictions.",
  "like": "Disciples, fruit wine, balance",
  "familiarData": "A dark elf woman in tattered clothing, looking as though she has suffered some tragedy. In reality, the clothes were slashed by her own sword aura. Her true identity is the current Sword Saint, one of the strongest beings on the continent.\n\nEccentric and impulsive, she strikes at anything that displeases her. She has no consistent standard for her actions -- she once switched sides to help the resistance army during a subjugation battle, only to destroy the resistance herself afterward. Her behavior is deeply contradictory.\n\nDue to her overwhelming power, those around her dare not voice their anger and only wish to stay away. Like temperamental nature itself, she has been dubbed a 'Natural Disaster'. The greatest contradiction is that despite acting on whims, she serves as the honorary president of an underground arena in the name of order.\n\nShe possesses the ability to grasp elements, able to condense moisture from the atmosphere into an ice blade at any time, ensuring she is never without a weapon.",
